      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it garaged and making sure every service was done right on time. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh new car smell. I'm so sad to see it go, but I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you\u2019re interested\u2014I\u2019d love to chat and show it to you!",
