    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and a fully serviced dual-VANOS system. This example delivers a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis is exceptional, with documented subframe reinforcement and a suspension refresh utilizing Bilstein dampers for surgical handling precision. Every mechanical system, including the rod bearings and cooling circuit, has been maintained to an exacting standard. This is a turn-key performance icon with zero deferred maintenance, preserved in showroom condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
